sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Server as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant AuthMW as Authentication<br/>Middleware
    participant JWKS as OIDC Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ABAC as Access Control<br/>(ABAC Engine)
    participant Router as Inference Router
    participant AgentRT as Agent Runtime
    participant SafetyProv as Safety Provider
    participant ToolRT as Tool Runtime (RAG)
    participant VectorProv as Vector I/O Provider
    participant InlineProv as Inline Provider<br/>(in-process)
    participant RemoteProv as Remote Provider<br/>(e.g., vLLM 8000/TCP)
    participant OTel as OpenTelemetry<br/>Collector

    Note over Client,OTel: Flow 1: Chat Completion Request

    Client->>Server: POST /v1/inference/chat-completion<br/>Auth: Bearer JWT
    Server->>Server: TracingMiddleware<br/>Extract W3C traceparent
    Server->>OTel: Log telemetry event (async)
    Server->>AuthMW: Validate Bearer token
    AuthMW->>JWKS: GET /.well-known/jwks.json<br/>TLS 1.2+
    JWKS-->>AuthMW: Public keys (cached)
    AuthMW->>AuthMW: Validate JWT signature & claims
    AuthMW->>ABAC: Check permit/forbid rules<br/>Principal, Action: create, Resource: inference
    ABAC-->>AuthMW: Authorized
    AuthMW-->>Server: User context set
    Server->>Router: Route to Inference provider

    alt Inline Provider (e.g., meta-reference)
        Router->>InlineProv: Direct in-process call
        InlineProv-->>Router: Completion result
    else Remote Provider (e.g., vLLM)
        Router->>RemoteProv: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, API key
        RemoteProv-->>Router: Completion result
    end

    Router-->>Server: Response
    Server-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>(or SSE stream for streaming)

    Note over Client,OTel: Flow 2: Agent Turn with RAG

    Client->>Server: POST /v1/agents/{id}/session/{sid}/turn<br/>Auth: Bearer JWT
    Server->>AuthMW: Validate token + ABAC check
    AuthMW-->>Server: Authorized
    Server->>AgentRT: Create agent turn

    AgentRT->>SafetyProv: Input shield check<br/>(Llama Guard / Prompt Guard)
    SafetyProv-->>AgentRT: Safe / Violation

    AgentRT->>Router: Chat completion (initial)<br/>Model determines tool use
    Router->>RemoteProv: POST /v1/chat/completions
    RemoteProv-->>Router: Tool call: knowledge_search
    Router-->>AgentRT: Tool call requested

    AgentRT->>ToolRT: Execute RAG query
    ToolRT->>VectorProv: Query similar chunks
    VectorProv->>Router: Generate embeddings
    Router->>RemoteProv: POST /v1/embeddings
    RemoteProv-->>Router: Embedding vectors
    Router-->>VectorProv: Vectors
    VectorProv-->>ToolRT: Matching chunks
    ToolRT-->>AgentRT: RAG context

    AgentRT->>Router: Chat completion (with RAG context)
    Router->>RemoteProv: POST /v1/chat/completions
    RemoteProv-->>Router: Final response
    Router-->>AgentRT: Response

    AgentRT->>SafetyProv: Output shield check
    SafetyProv-->>AgentRT: Safe

    AgentRT-->>Server: Agent turn result
    Server-->>Client: SSE stream response

    Note over Client,OTel: Flow 3: Evaluation Job

    Client->>Server: POST /v1/eval/benchmarks/{id}/jobs<br/>Auth: Bearer JWT
    Server->>AuthMW: Validate token + ABAC check
    AuthMW-->>Server: Authorized

    Server->>Server: Eval Provider: Load dataset
    Server->>Router: Generate responses per row
    Router->>RemoteProv: Batch inference calls
    RemoteProv-->>Router: Model outputs
    Router-->>Server: Responses collected
    Server->>Server: Scoring Provider: Score outputs
    Server-->>Client: Job ID

    Client->>Server: GET /v1/eval/benchmarks/{id}/jobs/{jid}/result
    Server-->>Client: Evaluation results
